The RNAseq data discussed in this publication have been deposited in NCBI’s Gene Expression Omnibus40 and are accessible through GEO Series accession number GSE212835. All other source data supporting the findings of this study are available within the paper and its Supplementary Information. Uncropped blots are provided as
Supplementary Fig. 8. Source data underlying the graphs and charts presented in the main figures are provided as Supplementary Data 1.
Received: 17 December 2022; Accepted: 3 October 2023;
